## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2a5ff-103">Na biblioteca de tipos a seguir, `OLE_COLOR` é um alias para `int`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a5ff-103">In the following type library,  `OLE_COLOR` is an alias for `int`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2a5ff-104">Durante a importação, os argumentos do `Color` acessador são marcados com o <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> para indicar a essa biblioteca de tipo refere-se a eles como `OLE_COLOR`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a5ff-104">During import, the arguments of the `Color` accessor are marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> to indicate that type library refers to them as `OLE_COLOR`.</span></span>  
  
```  
  
typedef int OLE_COLOR;    
  
interface Baz {  
 HRESULT SetColor([in] OLE_COLOR cl);  
 HRESULT GetColor([out, retval] OLE_COLOR *cl);  
}  
  
```  
  
